    "Word2Vec was employed for the embedding phase.",
    "Rumors are extracted from DataHeart database, upgraded and combined with own collected data.",
    "An automatic approach embedded in Chrome web browser is presented in Sahoo and Gupta (2021), with the goal of detecting fake news on Facebook.",
    "Specifically, Sahoo et al.",
    "leverage on Facebook account features combined with news content to analyze the account behavior through LSTM."
